{"title":"Unit 3: Lesson 4, Exercise B","clock":true,"countdown":0,"intro":{"buttons":{"start":"Start"},"content":[]},"activity":{"scenes":[{"block":"scene","name":"SC1","countdown":0,"instructions":{"open":true,"content":[{"block":"group","class":"flex gap-2 items-center","content":[{"block":"audio","class":"","file":"files/instruccion.mp3","wave":false,"autoplay":false,"id":"","name":"MfPG"},{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Read the passage and select the correct answer.","id":"","name":"MDJI"}]}]},"content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-3 my-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto","content":[{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center","content":[{"file":"files/img01.jpg","class":"mask mask-squircle w-3/4","id":"yzNO","block":"image","name":"zisY"}],"background":"","id":"mCGd","block":"group","name":"ttz4"},{"marker":"","class":"p-5 text-xl","content":[{"marker":"","class":"mt-10 ","content":[{"text":"Gloria was a famous singer. She was born in the U.S. but she had Mexican roots. Her first language was English, but she knew how to sing in Spanish as if she was a native speaker. When she was a kid, she used to pretend she had a band with her siblings, and eventually, she did.","class":"","id":"ILDG","block":"text","name":"Zhj2"}],"background":"","id":"z3wk","block":"group","name":"0Dat"},{"marker":"","class":"mt-5","content":[{"text":"Gloria began her career when she was quite young, but people could tell she was going to be a great star! She connected with the audience and it was easy for her to make them feel was she was feeling through her songs.","class":"","id":"ILDGxsWl","block":"text","name":"5U4U"}],"background":"","id":"UWG8jj3M","block":"group","name":"a7oh"},{"marker":"","class":"mt-5","content":[{"text":"Gloria had a lot of fans, and unfortunately, one of them was obsessed with her person, her lifestyle and fame. So, she pretended to be her friend and gained her trust. ","class":"","id":"ILDGxsWlh5Qi","block":"text","name":"7nME"}],"background":"","id